Experience the power of our smart formulated Frozen Essence GLOW MANIFESTO.

Luxurious, highly effective and deeply soothing. It’s a match made in skincare heaven.

Designed to be Frozen. 

GLOW MANIFESTO Key Ingredients List:

🌱Abyssine 
A molecule naturally derived from an extremophile living in deep-sea hydrothermal vents. Exoplysaccharide soothes sensitive skin and relieves discomfort. 

🌱Tephrosia Purpurea Seed Extract
With its calming, radiance-enhancing, anti-stress, and anti-pollutant properties, this active botanical fights signs of fatigue & tiredness and promotes release of relaxing neuropeptides to reduce skin redness. 

🧬Potassium Azeloyl Diglycinate
This active ingredient is a water-soluble derivative of azelaic acid that hydrates, illuminates skin, evens out complexion and improves skin elasticity.

🌹 Rosa Damascena Flower Water
Skin-soothing & refreshing rose floral water reduces redness and calms the senses. 

🧬Fruit Acids (Malic, Tartaric, Citric, Glycolic, Lactic Acids) 
 They help exfoliate, brighten, and improve tone and texture.

🧬Tourmaline
With energizing properties and a reputation for improving blood circulation, this precious gemstone is believed to purify and transform dense energy.

TURN ŌN YOUR SKIN POTENTIAL ™

Today, as I celebrate another year of life, I am reminded of the preciousness of this gift we all share.

I am asking you to join me in supporting the Breast Cancer Research Foundation.  This is not just a charity, but a beacon of hope for millions of women and men around the world. Every dollar we donate brings us one step closer to a world where no one has to lose a loved one to breast cancer.

By donating to the Breast Cancer Research Foundation, we are not just giving money, we are giving hope, strength, and most importantly, we are giving life.

 Because every life is precious, and every life is worth fighting for. Right?

Thank you 🥰
